{"tid":2489753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台兼職記者涉嫌刑事罪被捕 港台會全面配合警方調查並即時停職","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:12:16.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"79c48646d5596165d57b9456647479b4238e5a85","tid":2489753,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"香港電台確認一名兼職初級記者今早涉嫌刑事罪被捕。港台發言人說，<strong>會全面配合警方的調查，並已即時停止該名兼職員工的職務。</strong><br />\n<br />\n警方今早在港鐵海洋公園站，拘捕一名22歲男子，在他的背包中搜出兩支玩具槍及對講機，將他帶返香港仔警署調查。警方指，男子報稱是知專設計學院的電影系學生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585922-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585922-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=b08b37ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585922-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=86b5553f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585922-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ac0a0d8d0831c2cac4151588d0beee60544774cb","tid":2489753,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"新港共台第一時間出聲明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a09795dcc6bb5e8f503d38ee1b4cebfeeba4cb8","tid":2489753,"uid":28913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ac0a0d8d0831c2cac4151588d0beee60544774cb","tid":2489753,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"新港共台第一時間出聲明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />